net.javacoding.jspider.api.event
Interface EventVisitor

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlatOutputPlugin, StatusBasedFileWriterPlugin
public interface EventVisitor

Visitor interface that must be implemented upon each class that will act as a visitor in the applied visitor pattern for event handling. This interface contains a visit method for each JSpider API event type. $Id: EventVisitor.java,v 1.6 2003/04/08 15:50:24 vanrogu Exp $

Author:
Günther Van Roey
